success.name: MITRE ATT&CK Cloud - Full Coverage
success.description: The MITRE ATT&CK Cloud - Full coverage scenario includes attacks that assess the environment's risk in the face of various cloud TTPs, as detailed in the MITRE ATT&CK Cloud matrix framework. It includes representative attacks that are mapped to the cloud-related techniques within the MITRE ATT&CK enterprise framework. Use this scenario as a comprehensive way to benchmark your cloud-related security posture.

success.name: Enterprise Baseline
success.description: The Enterprise Baseline scenario includes attacks that validate the security posture of enterprise networks, including a variety of attack techniques, spread across the MITRE ATT&CK framework and a selection of top 10 malware threats. Use this scenario as a quick and consistent way to validate your enterprise network security posture.
